# CC nav bake checkpoint

When rebaking or tuning castle (`Cc_*`) nav meshes:

1. Read `Tools/nav_bake_checkpoint_cc.json` (summary: `Tools/NAV_BAKE_CHECKPOINT_CC.md`).
2. Use profile `cc_baseline_v1` unless the target group has `env_overrides` / a different `param_profile`.
3. Clear leftover `NAV_EXPERIMENT_*` env vars, then set only `explicit_env` (+ that group's overrides).
4. Rebake with the group's `tiles` (1x1 single `--tile`, 2x2 `--combined --combined-name`).
5. Compare against `golden_glb` / `golden_regions_glb` under `golden_out`.
6. When a tuned override sticks, write it into `groups[].env_overrides` and note the new profile name.
